text: > Sports Dodgers and Mattingly part ways in mutual agreement FILE - In this Oct. 12, 2015, file photo, Los Angeles Dodgers manager Don Mattingly arrives for a news conference before Game 3 of baseballâ€™s National League Division Series against the New York Mets at CitiField in New York.
